  "title": "Business Development Lead/Partner Manager (AdTech)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Business Development Lead/Partner Manager (Adtech)</strong><br /><br /><strong>Responsibility</strong></p><ul><li>Develop Strong partnership with our key demand partners across APAC</li><li>Work closely with internal teams (Legal, Finance, Operations Product) to structure deals that maximize revenue</li><li>Forecast revenue and manage a pipeline of potential and current business</li><li>Prepare and execute on customer success plans. Drive a full sales cycle pipeline, pitching and closing business</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 2+ years of experienced in the adtech space</li><li>Bachelor's degree in any field</li><li>strong client facing experience in a similar industry</li></ul><p>Regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br />www.dadaconsultants.com<br />EA Registration Number: R1878287<br />Business Registration Number: 201735941W.<br /></p><p></p><p></p>",
